{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"white","bgm":"bgm20_song10","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":300}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"...In the end...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"During Miss Livia's interview,@I ended up talking more than she did..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":1,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"Even so, the shadow that Miss Livia carries..."},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"I feel like I've touched on a little bit of it."},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"So, in the end, I think it was a valuable interview@experience."},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"And then, the next group I visited was..."},{"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","nameNarration":"","narration":"<Neo-Magius>","narrationBg":"black","narrationEffect":"in"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_15053.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":103001,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102901,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"bgm":"bgm23_magus02","chara":[{"id":103001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameRight":"Hagumu","textRight":"...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":103001}],"nameRight":"Hagumu","textRight":"As expected, when you come to this spot,@you can really feel it..."},{"chara":[{"id":102901}],"nameLeft":"Shigure","textLeft":"...Yeah."},{"chara":[{"id":102901,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Shigure","textLeft":"It was just a little while ago, wasn't it?"},{"chara":[{"id":103001,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"Hagumu","textRight":"...Yeah."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":1,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"Umm...are you sure you're okay with this place?@If you're going to talk, we could go somewhere else..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp3.json","id":103001,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Hagumu","textLeft":"This location is better. How can I put it..."},{"chara":[{"id":103001}],"nameLeft":"Hagumu","textLeft":"We think we can properly express ourselves here."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102901,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shigure","textLeft":"Facing what happened in the past, yeah..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"...Right..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":103001,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Hagumu","textLeft":"Should we start by talking about our current@situation?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102001}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"Yes, please."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":103001,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Hagumu","textLeft":"...Actually, up until recently..."},{"chara":[{"id":103001}],"nameLeft":"Hagumu","textLeft":"We were on the verge of falling apart. "},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":400,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"...Does that mean the Neo-Magius was about to@disband?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102901,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shigure","textLeft":"Yes..."},{"chara":[{"id":102901}],"nameLeft":"Shigure","textLeft":"Princess tried to kill every Magical Girl@that wasn't part of our group..."},{"chara":[{"id":102901}],"nameLeft":"Shigure","textLeft":"And now everyone knows that..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102901,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Shigure","textLeft":"After that, the Feathers lost heart@and started pulling away..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":103001,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Hagumu","textLeft":"We thought that they would all leave."},{"chara":[{"id":103001}],"nameLeft":"Hagumu","textLeft":"After all, she tried to do something heinous..."},{"chara":[{"id":103001,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Hagumu","textLeft":"Normally, people would hesitate to follow someone@like that..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"...I see..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102901,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shigure","textLeft":"We were already prepared for the possibility@that we could cease to function as a group."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":103001,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Hagumu","textLeft":"We thought it was inevitable..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":102901,"motion":200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shigure","textLeft":"But then, someone stepped up to try to@prevent that collapse."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"...Who?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":103001,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Hagumu","textLeft":"The same person who pushed the Neo-Magius@to the brink of disbandment."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102901,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shigure","textLeft":"It was Princess."},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":400}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"Himena?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":102901}],"nameLeft":"Shigure","textLeft":"Yep..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp3.json","id":103001,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Hagumu","textLeft":"We were surprised by how enthusiastic she was... "},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
